sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant CL as cleaner.py
    participant PR as profiler.py
    participant EDA as eda.py
    participant AN as analyzer.py
    participant DI as domain_insights.py

    User->>UI: Upload CSV / Load Sample
    UI->>UI: Store raw_df in session state

    UI->>CL: raw_df
    CL->>CL: Normalize columns
    CL->>CL: Remove duplicates
    CL->>CL: Fix data types (strip $, convert strings)
    CL->>CL: Detect missing values
    CL->>UI: Missing summary + outlier info
    User->>UI: Choose fill strategy per column
    User->>UI: Choose outlier action per column
    User->>UI: Click "Apply Cleaning"
    UI->>CL: Apply strategies
    CL->>UI: cleaned_df + CleaningReport

    UI->>PR: cleaned_df
    PR->>PR: Classify columns (numeric/categorical/datetime/id)
    PR->>PR: Detect domain from column keywords
    PR->>PR: Compute quality score (0-100)
    PR->>UI: domain, quality_score, col_types

    UI->>EDA: cleaned_df
    EDA->>UI: Correlation heatmap (Plotly)
    EDA->>UI: Distribution charts per column
    EDA->>UI: Category bar charts

    User->>UI: Select analysis type + columns
    UI->>AN: cleaned_df + selected columns
    AN->>AN: Pearson correlation + p-value
    AN->>AN: Group aggregation
    AN->>AN: StandardScaler + LinearRegression
    AN->>AN: OLS hypothesis testing
    AN->>UI: Coefficients, R², p-values, CIs

    UI->>DI: cleaned_df + domain
    DI->>DI: Compute domain KPIs
    DI->>DI: Filter winning ads / top products / budget variance / attrition
    DI->>UI: Domain-specific tables + metrics

    UI->>User: Full interactive dashboard
